                            <comment id="12663" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Tue, 22 Mar 2005 02:03:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for spotting this! The question is: how can we work around this issue? One option might be to perform the startsWith comparison on a lower-case requestUri, with a lower-case contextPath. That might actually work in all cases; I guess I&apos;ll give that a try.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Juergen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
